headline: JPMorgan Lowers W.W. Grainger (GWW) PT to $1,035 Amidst Mixed Q2 Results, Gross Margin Pressure.
summary: W.W. Grainger Inc. (NYSE:GWW) is one of the stocks to invest in before they split next. On September 4, JPMorgan lowered the firm’s price target on W.W. Grainger Inc. (NYSE:GWW) to $1,035 from $1,125, while maintaining a Neutral rating on the shares. JPMorgan updated the estimates for the US distributors to reflect the recent earnings […]
